&lt;p&gt;We are excited to be offering this new post for an Emotional and Health Wellbeing Nurse for our Care Leavers in Newham.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a dynamic and enthusiastic person to join the Children Looked After Team. You will be an experienced health professional with proven experience of working in the mental health field with adolescents and young people. The post will work closely with Newham CFCS and Childrens Social Care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post will initially be involved with the 18-21yr Care Leavers, but we will be looking to expand to 18-25yr as the post becomes embedded.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
